  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-12 col-md-7">
      <br />
      <h2>Your source for mythical creatures in Berlin</h2>
      <p>
        We are your experts for legendary beasts. You donâ€™t know which food your basilisk really needs?
        You wonder which type of brush is right for your Medusa's hair?
        You are looking for a companion for your gryphon?
        Then this is the place to be!
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-12 col-md-5" style="padding-left: 20px;">
